  6  1. Free magma of a type (traversable, decidable equality).
  7  2. Free semigroup of a magma.
  8  3. Free semigroup of a type (traversable, decidable equality).
  9  
 10  And finally, magma.free_semigroup (free_magma α) ≃ free_semigroup α.
 11  -/
